{"tid":1023130,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實做YouTuber 係咪好好搵？","createTime":"2019-02-15T13:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T09:49:01.000Z","uid":207358,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c855abf54e9b3d9ff3ad3110ed2623b7694ee465","tid":1023130,"uid":207358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:56:34.000Z","msg":"早排睇完sunny 果條年宵攤檔片，見佢賣自己果d產品好賣得，但我其實唔係好明點解d人會咁瘋狂咁買佢d產品。<br />\n大多數買家都係20歲以下，年輕人為主。明明佢地理論上係無番工，無乜經濟能力，但係佢地就係買得最多野。<br />\n睇到最後有個後生仔（好似係18歲）同一個小朋友爭住買個紙牌，最後個紙牌價值為$650，睇到果度我真係唔明點解d人會捨得買，究竟佢地d錢係咪真係多到買地方洗。<br />\n我呢個post 唔係想針對sunny,佢的確係有努力拍片掙錢。我想帶出點嘅係解依家d人會願意花咁多錢去支持佢地心目中所謂嘅偶像，究竟d家長係咪比好多錢佢地嘅仔女，等佢地去亂咁洗錢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ycbq4Cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYcbq4Cb.png&h=fd4bfb69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O23Udvx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO23Udvx.png&h=1675a647&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rMq4Cc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rMq4Cc.png&h=2307ae7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07ee525b1a6c0c83b84e543f10e410f573f57a50","tid":1023130,"uid":769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:58:02.000Z","msg":"而家d中學生中中一杯珍珠奶茶點會冇錢"},{"pid":"3b9e13a912854cce7ad03f54d0a242d3a75510c7","tid":1023130,"uid":769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:58:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家d中學生<span style=\"color: brown;\">日日</span>一杯珍珠奶茶點會冇錢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9dfc5c324e1fc6aa843454eefc3db7fc533864e","tid":1023130,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:00:21.000Z","msg":"幾百蚊算少啦&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n莫講依家<br />\n對十幾年前嘅中學生嚟講都濕濕碎啦"},{"pid":"5e2a0daa056761cf07e37305a5111322dbabe17f","tid":1023130,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"